{start_of_verse: 主歌/Couplet}
壓傷的蘆葦祂不折斷，將殘的蠟燭祂不吹熄，   yā shāng de lú wěi tā bù zhé duàn jiāng cán de là zhú tā bù chuī xī
[bruised]  [and]  [with-ered]  [reed,]  [He]  [will]  [—]  [not]  [break.]  [A]  [dim-]  [ly]  [burn-ing]  [flame，]  [—He]  [will]  [—]  [not]  [quench.-]  [—]  [The]
